<p class="">Resolved,</p><p class=""> <blockquote><q>"That a Select Committee be appointed to investigate the conduct and activities of Mr. Boothby in connection with the payment out of assets in this country of claims against the <span id="831" class="column-number" data-column-number="831"></span> Government of and institutions in the Republic of Czechoslovakia: to report generally on these matters and in particular to consider and report whether the conduct of the honourable Member was contrary to the usage or derogatory to the dignity of the House or inconsistent with the standards which Parliament is entitled to expect from its Members."</q></blockquote></p>
